desmoj.extensions.dimensions

Class Quantity

  • java.lang.Object
    • desmoj.extensions.dimensions.Quantity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Units, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Duration, Length, Velocity
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public abstract class Quantity
extends java.lang.Object
implements Units, java.lang.Comparable
    An abstract base class for physical quantities with a unit (e.g. Length, Velocity, etc.).
